# {{ project_name }} - JupyterHub Deployment

Local deployment overlay of [stellars-jupyterhub-ds](https://github.com/stellarshenson/stellars-jupyterhub-ds), generated from the [deployment template](https://github.com/stellarshenson/stellars-jupyterhub-ds-deployment-template).

## Overview

- Multi-user JupyterHub 4 platform with GPU support and NativeAuthenticator
- {{ project_name }} branding (logo, JupyterLab top-bar icon, browser favicon)
- Local Traefik reverse proxy with self-signed TLS certificates

## Access

- `BASE_HOSTNAME={{ base_hostname }}` - root domain
- `JUPYTERHUB_PREFIX={{ jupyterhub_subdomain_prefix }}` - subdomain prefix (empty = root)

Default URL: `https://{{ jupyterhub_subdomain_prefix }}{{ base_hostname }}/`

Override either value via `.env` (untracked).

